::Battera::

She awaoke from her sleep.  She opened her eyes and looked around.  
She sat up and stretched her arms and wings.  She felt suprizingly 
better than when she hat entered her sleep. She got up and walked 
around her room to work out the kinks in her legs.  She opened the 
door to her room and walked out.  She headed for the bridge.  She 
woould give the coordinants of the embassy to the maximals.  Then she 
would ask for a position on the crew until the talks would commense.  
She folded her wings around her like a cloke and walked down the hall 
towards the bridge.
